title.en: Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
Hakushaku Reijou no Konyakusha wa Itsumo Shio Taiou, Unzari shita no de Shio Taiou Kaeshi Hajimemasu
Gimai ga Seijo dakara to Konyakuhaki Saremashita ga, Watashi wa Yousei no Itoshigo desu
Kinou made Namae mo Yonde Kurenakatta Koushaku-sama ga, Kyuu ni Dekiai shitekuru no desu ga?
Ochikobore Reijou wa, Koushaku Kakka kara no Dekiai ni Kizukanai ~Konyakusha ni Shimeisareta no wa Saishoku Kenbi no Ane de wa Naku, Watashi deshita~
Konyaku Haki Shita Aite ga Mainichi Shazai ni Kimasu ga, Fukuen Nante Zettai ni Ariemasen!
Watashi, Seijo. Ima, Kankinsarete Iru no
Seiryaku Kekkon no Otto ni "Aisanakute Kekkou desu" to Sengen Shitara Dekiai ga Hajimarimashita
Kono Ai wa, Kokuou Heika no Gomeirei Janai - Ohitori-sama Kibou no Reijou desu ga, Funaka na Kishi ga Hanashitekuremasen!
Seijo no Ane desu ga, Naze ka Miwaku no Koushaku-sama ni Tsukaeru Koto ni narimashita
Tensei Jijou no Chiebukuro - "Jishou" Hitonami Kaishain deshita ga, Zense no Chishiki de Karei ni Otsukae Itashimasu!
Enzai Reijou wa Shinjitai - Ginpatsu ga Fukitsu to Iwarete Konyaku Hakisareta Shishaku Reijou wa Ansatsu Kizoku ni Dekiaisarete Daini no Jinsei wo Tannou suru you desu
Zense Watashi ni Kyoumi ga Nakatta Otto, Chara Hen shite Dekiai shite Kite mo Taiou ni Komarimasu!
Honmono no Seijo Janai to Bareta no ni, Outei Denka ni Semararete imasu
Konyakusha ga Uwaki Aite to Kakeochi shimashita. Ouji Denka ni Dekiaisarete Shiawase na no de, Imasara Modoritai to Iwarete mo Komarimasu
Migawari Konyaku Shananoni, Gin Ookami Heika ga Doushitemo Hanashite Kuremasen!
Kishi Danchou wa Dansou Joshi ga Hoshikute Tamaranai - Kono Dekiai Okashikunai desu ka?
